body_html:
Letters, like the alphabet? Something's up.

DODGEBALL CXXXVI - the 136th - crashes the Wall High School tennis courts for yet another action-packed, three-hour massacre presented by EastCoastDodgeball. The main attraction for this spectacular will be announced live on May 3.

The is undoubtedly one of the most crucial time periods in the history of the sport, and the Season 14 finale much reason why. Remember, DODGEBALL CXL team generals Juan Londono and Justin Wolf will no longer be allowed to combine their unlimited resources. It should be very interesting to see what happens during this time.
